item.title: Pushing Delta 3200
item.description: Unless you’re interested in reading why I like fast film, you can skip to this section for how I actually develop it. That’s the part that covers what made me want to write this in the first place. I kept losing my notes so this will actually serve as a long-winded note-to-self. If you want to skip to some pictures, see results. Historical context Around 2007, I got pretty into photography.
